@startuml
hide empty members
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

title US222 - Domain Model (DM) Sub-domain

class Aircraft {
    - registrationNumber
    - totalFlightHours
    - status
    - manufacturingDate
}

class AircraftModel {
    - modelName
}

class MaintenanceTemplate {
    - templateName
    - flightHoursInterval
    - calendarDaysInterval
}

class MaintenanceRecord {
    - completionDate
    - status
}

Aircraft "*" --> "1" AircraftModel : is of type >
MaintenanceTemplate "*" --> "*" AircraftModel : applies to >
Aircraft "1" <-- "*" MaintenanceRecord : performed on <

note right of MaintenanceTemplate
  Contains the intervals used to
  evaluate if an Aircraft is due
  for scheduled maintenance.
end note

note right of MaintenanceRecord
  Used to determine the days passed
  since the last completed maintenance.
end note

@enduml